  strCategory: "Vegetarian",
  strArea: "British",
  strInstructions: "Soak the dried mushrooms in 350ml boiling water and set aside until needed. Blitz ¾ of the chestnuts with 150ml water until creamy. Roughly chop the remaining chestnuts.
